  "text": "Strains Schizochytrium limacinum PA-968 and Japonochytrium marinum AN-4 were deposited in the culture collection of the Department of Biochemistry and Microbiology, University of Chemistry and Technology Prague. These strains were maintained in ATCC790 By + medium [CITATION_1] .",
